{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"你当赞颂你至高主的大名超绝万物，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"他创造万物并使各物匀称。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他预定万物，而加以引导。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"他生出牧草，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"然后使它变成黑色的枯草。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"我将使你诵读，故你不会忘记，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"除非安拉所欲忘记的。他的确知道显著的和隐微的言行。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"我将使你遵循平易的道路，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"故你当教诲众人，如果教诲有裨于他们的话。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"畏主的人，将觉悟；"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"薄命的人，将退避，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"他将入于大火，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"然后，在火里不死也不活。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"纯洁者必定成功，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"他记念他的主的尊名，而谨守拜功。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"不然，你们却选择今世的生活；"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"其实，后世是更好的，是更长久的。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"这确是载在古经典中的，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"载在易卜拉欣和穆萨的经典中的。"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"大灾的消息，确已降临你了，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"在那日，将有许多人是恭敬的、"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"劳动的、辛苦的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"他们将入烈火，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"将饮沸泉，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他们没有食物，但有荆棘，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"既不肥人，又不能充饥；"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"在那日，将有许多人，是享福的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"是为其劳绩而愉快的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"他们将在崇高的乐园中，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"听不到恶言，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"里面有流泉，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"里面有高榻，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"有陈设着的杯盏，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"有排列着的靠枕，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"有铺展开的绒毯。"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"难道他们不观察吗？骆驼是怎样造成的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"天是怎样被升高的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"山峦是怎样被竖立起的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"大地是怎样被展开的。"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"你当教诲，你只是教诲（他们的），"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"你绝不是监察他们的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"但谁转身离去而且不信教，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"安拉将以最大的刑罚惩治谁。"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"他们必定只归于我，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"他们的稽核，必定由我负责。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"誓以黎明，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"与十夜，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"与偶数和奇数，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"与离去的黑夜，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"对于有理智者，此中有一种盟誓吗？"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"难道你不知道你的主怎样惩治阿德人——"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"有高柱的伊赖姆人吗？"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"像那样的人，在别的城市里还没有被创造过的——"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"怎样惩治在山谷里凿石为家的赛莫德人，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"怎样惩治有武力的法老。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"这等人曾在国中放肆，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"乃多行不义，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"故你的主把一种刑罚，倾注在他们身上。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"你的主，确是监视的。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"至于人，当他的主考验他，故优待他，而且使他过安逸的生活的时候，他说：“我的主优待我了。”"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"当他考验他，故节约他的给养的时候，他说：“我的主凌辱我了。”"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"绝不然！但你们不优待孤儿，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"你们不以济贫相勉励，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"你们侵吞遗产，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"你们酷爱钱财。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"绝不然！当大地震动复震动，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"你的主和整列整列的天使，同齐来临的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"在那日，火狱将被拿来；在那日，人将觉悟，但觉悟于他有何裨益呢？"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"他将说：“但愿我在世的时候曾行善事。”"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"在那日，任何人，不用他的那种刑罚惩治别人；"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"任何人，不用他的那种束缚束缚别人。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"安定的灵魂啊！"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"你应当喜悦地，被喜悦地归于你的主。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"你应当入在我的众仆里；"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"你应当入在我的乐园里。"}]}